            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間27日10:30，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲105.7點（或1.33%），暫報8032.74點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+1.78%</li><li>近 1 月：+10.06%</li><li>近 3 月：+10.67%</li><li>近 6 月：+40.51%</li><li>今年以來：+7.68%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以格羅方德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GFS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GFS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GFS-US</a>)領漲。格羅方德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GFS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GFS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GFS-US</a>)上漲4.46%；美光科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>)上漲4.02%；科林研發(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LRCX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LRCX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LRCX-US</a>)上漲3.48%；英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)上漲3.15%；芯源系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MPWR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MPWR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MPWR-US</a>)上漲2.8%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，安森美半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ON:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ON\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ON-US</a>)下跌1.47%；安謀控股公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ARM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ARM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ARM-US</a>)下跌1.41%；德州儀器(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TXN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TXN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TXN-US</a>)下跌0.97%；應用材料(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMAT-US</a>)下跌0.88%；科沃(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QRVO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QRVO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QRVO-US</a>)下跌0.28%。</p></section></main>",
